com.estimote.sdk.cloud

Interface CloudCallback<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - Response type.

    public interface CloudCallback<T>
    Communicates response from a server or an error. Only one method will be invoked in response to a given request.

    Callback methods are executed on application's main thread.
